The,Signpost,API,provides,programmatic,access,to,the,Signpost,CRM,and,marketing,platform,It,is,designed,to,help,local,businesses,get,feedback,new,customers,referrals,reviews,and,repeat,business,Signpost,helps,businesses,optimize,their,online,profiles,and,automatically,collects,and,stores,customer,data,which,is,then,used,to,power,its,remarketing,engine